        <mxCell id="legend_text" value="&lt;font color=&quot;#555&quot;&gt;❶ User submits prompt in Streamlit UI&lt;br&gt;❷ UI POSTs JSON to FastAPI /supervisor/query&lt;br&gt;❸ ApiRoutes delegates to Supervisor.query()&lt;br&gt;❹ Supervisor loads state (per conversation_id)&lt;br&gt;❺ Jinja2 template renders prompt with history&lt;br&gt;❻ &lt;b&gt;asyncio.gather()&lt;/b&gt; fans out to all enabled agents&lt;br&gt;❼ Each agent calls its cloud LLM provider&lt;br&gt;❽ Responses fan-in; state is saved&lt;br&gt;❾ AggregationTool synthesizes via GPT&lt;br&gt;❿ SupervisorResponse returned → UI renders cards&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
